The mods compilation in the archive is broken by last mod (zeRobuRn's MobSpawnerCrafting) that i somehow had it working or fooled myself that i had somehow and discovered later that it doesn't work while fiddling around.

http://www.filefront.com/17734962/126-strawberry-mods-compilation.zip/

SlowFallBoots was creating invincibility instead. Updated:

http://www.filefront.com/17735342/126-strawberry-mods-compilation.zip/
Seems to work fine now, only snag it will crash once at first when opening the inventory, but after you reload the world it's stable.

You also need to copy mods\zombe dir and contents from compilation to .minecraft dir instead of the minecraft.jar to make Graves mod work, else you'll only find empty ones. The author decided to not do it like everybody else :-/
